metadata.name: Generic Giraffe #1
metadata.description: Generic Giraffe Club is a collection of 10k randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. Our goal is to build the biggest herd to connect giraffes from all around the world for life. Each Generic Giraffe isn’t just a cool PFP it’s your pass to exclusive events, monthly reflections to all Giraffes, treasury backed daily lottery, donations and more. This is just the beginning so join the herd.
